Dorothy Van https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Van 0 Dorothy Van (January 10, 1928 - May 16, 2002) was an American stage and TV actress who is best remembered for her comedic role as Aunt Effie Harper on the 1980s situation comedy Mama's Family.
